name: Go beyond work with Linus Lee, Daniela Petruzalek, & Sebastian Spaink (Go Time #212)
summary: Our final installment from GopherCon 2021 is an awesome panel conversation led by Natalie &amp; Angelica with guests Linus Lee, Daniela Patruzalek, and Sebastian Spank. All three of these gophers are using Go in cool and interesting ways outside of traditional work projects.
